WEBVTT

00:02:59.517 --> 00:03:01.252
And in the past few years, we've been able

00:03:01.252 --> 00:03:03.875
to propagate this lie even further

00:03:03.875 --> 00:03:06.149
via social media.

00:03:06.149 --> 00:03:08.382
You may have seen images like this one:

00:03:08.382 --> 00:03:11.985
"The only disability in life is a bad attitude."

00:03:12.975 --> 00:03:17.326
Or this one: "Your excuse is invalid." Indeed.

00:03:17.326 --> 00:03:23.686
Or this one: "Before you quit, try!"

00:03:23.686 --> 00:03:25.342
These are just a couple of examples,

00:03:25.342 --> 00:03:27.311
but there are a lot of these images out there.

00:03:27.311 --> 00:03:28.940
You know, you might have seen the one,

00:03:28.940 --> 00:03:30.689
the little girl with no hands